comment:
I‚Äôm a woman who was married to a narcissistic sociopath. They start out so wonderful and loving. They take center stage before you even realize it they start gaslighting you tearing you down isolating you. You don‚Äôt know what is truth anymore. You start to look terrible and aged very quickly. They make you feel guilty. 
I‚Äôm out of that mess 10 years ago. It takes time to heal but you come out of it stronger. 
I only shared all of that to say from the looks of Johnny, he‚Äôs been dragged through the same thing. When he said to the reporters that he was confused scared and just wanted to go home. He said that publicly for a reason.

The man has no history of violence according to the two previous women who shared a large part of their lives with him. Amber however does have a history of being abusive. 
I feel so sad for him that he had to go through this publicly. However the good thing is that it shows that women can be extremely abusive towards men and too often they get a free pass. She is a very nasty Jezebel. Thank God he didn‚Äôt have any kids with her!
I hope this judge gives her the maximum punishment she can get. 
She needed to be exposed for her atrocious behavior. I don‚Äôt even think she is pretty at all. The bitchy nastiness just oozes out of her and makes her extremely ugly. 
You will heal quickly. Even fans that adore you may be strangers to you, but I know they are sending kindness your way. 
Thanks for taking one for the team ( the people who got trapped into this psychotic mess). 
She needs to be locked up and then never work in the movie industry again.
